title: Lebowski's Bi-Monthly Poker Night
desc: Fun, low-stakes poker night every two weeks.  Time to drink white-russians, play cards and use The Big Lebowski quotes whenever possible. Dudes and Special lady friends welcome. Please RSVP and bring a toe. If you can get a toe. If you can't, I can get you a toe.  Bring a friend if you want just let me know.
